PROHIBITED USES:
1. Unauthorized interception of communications
2. Any use that violates local, state, federal, or international law
3. Commercial exploitation without explicit permission
4. Malicious activities of any kind
5. Production deployment

CONDITIONS:
- The above copyright notice and this permission notice shall be included in
